{
  "stem": "1799.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 684.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that prompted two of, two of the boys that were with me in that camp, because of the hunger-- and one of them was a bed wetter, even though he was 16-- to resort to eating food out of trash cans.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they promptly got, both of them, got sick, and died.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was, oh, maybe seven, eight weeks after we were in that camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I witnessed them dying myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that left only, that left only two besides me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was only a month or so after we were in the first camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One, Barron [INAUDIBLE], and the other one Arnold [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kachinski. ?] That was part of the group that had really cemented ties in the home that I mentioned in Chabannes in central France after the first stage of the war, and because of the commonality of education and of, of, like, a family life.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so that was my first experience of death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it wasn't killing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was just precipitated by lack of hygiene.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was to witness killing and other types of death later in large measure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there for several weeks until the onset of winter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember having been transferred to another camp called Graditz, which was to the north and to the west of there, where we were transported by-- I believe it was buses.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Graditz, I worked a night shift in a factory that was making ammunition.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we started working, like, at 9:00 in the evening, and it was, you know, until at least-- it was at least 12 hours of work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every day.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were just terrible conditions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, there was no normal food.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
